# Requests del caso de uso DeactivateWorkflow (tRPC MUTATION). Pone isActive=false.
# Requiere la extensión "REST Client" (humao.rest-client): clic en "Send Request".
# Levantá la API antes:  pnpm exec nx serve @org/api
# Pegá un id real (de un create) en @id.

@host = http://localhost:3001
@id = 00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000

### ✅ Desactivar (reemplazá @id por uno real) → 200 + DTO con "isActive": false
POST {{host}}/trpc/workflow.deactivate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{id}}"
}

### ❌ id inexistente → 404 NOT_FOUND
POST {{host}}/trpc/workflow.deactivate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000"
}

### ❌ id vacío → 400 (lo frena Zod: min(1))
POST {{host}}/trpc/workflow.deactivate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": ""
}
